The paper discusses optimizing the performance and power consumption of cloud resources, specifically multi-FPGA platforms, which suggests that it could belong to the categories of Architecture (cs.AR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Emerging Technologies (cs.ET), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
